title: We're Going To Europe
description:
Laura, RGIII, Marcus, Darlington, and Mel discuss the recently released NFL International schedule for the 2020 season, Brian Daboll’s comments on Daniel Jones, what is the Jets ceiling, Ryan Tannehill’s comments, Deebo Samuel’s future, and Marcus’ top 5 rookie edge rushers.
